<%- include ('components/_studentInfo') %>

<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/paginationjs/2.0.8/pagination.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jqueryui/1.12.1/jquery-ui.min.css">  <!--使用 jQuery 的 Tooltip-->

<h2 class="text-center title">聯合分發志願</h2>

<hr>

<div class="row" id="form-placementSelect">
	<div class="col-12">
		<div class="alert alert-warning" role="alert">
			請選填 <strong class="text-danger">聯合分發</strong> 志願，最多 <strong class="text-danger">70</strong> 個。
		</div>
		<div class="alert alert-danger hide" role="alert" id="not-to-FF">
			由於您已選擇不分發至臺師大僑先部，因此將無法選填「臺師大僑先部」志願。<span id="not-to-FF-link">如欲修改請<a href="/grade.html">點這裡</a>並勾選同意。</span>
		</div>

		<a class="btn btn-success quota-button" id="btn-group1Quota" href="#" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i> 第一類組名額查詢</a>
		<a class="btn btn-success quota-button" id="btn-group2Quota" href="#" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i> 第二類組名額查詢</a>
		<a class="btn btn-success quota-button" id="btn-group3Quota" href="#" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i> 第三類組名額查詢</a>

		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-12">
				<div class="card">
					<div class="card-header bg-primary text-white">注意事項</div>
					<div class="card-body">
						<p>
							欲申請醫學、牙醫、及中醫學系者，其最近連續居留海外／港澳需 8 年以上。
						</p>
						<p>
							醫學、牙醫、及中醫學系以 <mark class="bg-medical">黃底</mark> 標註。
						</p>
						<div class="MI-directions">
							<strong>系所類型 重要説明</strong>
						    <div><span class="badge badge-warning">重點產業系所</span></div>
							<ol>
								<li>
									選填【重點產業系所】校系志願者，請檢附華語文能力測驗(TOCFL)基礎級(A2)以上之證明，或達前開程度之中文能力證明文件。例如:「歷年成績單(含中文科目成績)」、「各類會考之中文成績或證明」、「就讀學校以中文授課證明」、其他足以佐證個人中文能力資料等。
								</li>
							</ol>
						</div>
						<div>
							<strong>操作說明</strong>
							<ol>
								<li>
									先於左欄招生校系清單以「志願代碼」、「類組」、「學群」、「學校名稱」、「系所名稱」或「系所類型」查詢，點選 <span class="badge badge-info"><i class="fa fa-plus" aria-hidden="true"></i></span> 將志願加入右欄。
								</li>
								<li>
									於右欄可以點選 <span class="badge badge-danger"><i class="fa fa-times" aria-hidden="true"></i></span> 刪除志願；以 <span class="badge badge-white"><i class="fa fa-chevron-up" aria-hidden="true"></i></span> <span class="badge badge-white"><i class="fa fa-chevron-down" aria-hidden="true"></i></span> 或直接輸入志願序調整志願順序。
								</li>
								<li>
									於左欄招生校系清單點選 <span class="badge badge-secondary"><i class="fa fa-list-ul" aria-hidden="true"></i></span> 可以查看系所招生資訊。
								</li>
								<li>
									最多可選填 <strong class="text-danger">70</strong> 個志願，除二、三類組得互跨類組選填志願外，其餘皆不得跨類組選填志願。
								</li>
							</ol>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<hr>

		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-xl-6">
				<div class="card card-bottom">
					<div class="card-header">招生校系清單</div>
					<div class="card-body">
						<div class="row">
							<div class="col-5">
								<select class="custom-select mb-2 mr-sm-2 mb-sm-0" id="select-optionFilter">
									<option value="cardCode">志願代碼</option>
									<option value="group">類組</option>
									<option value="mainGroup">學群</option>
									<option value="school">學校名稱</option>
									<option value="dept">系所名稱</option>
									<option value="type">系所類型</option>
								</select>
							</div>
							<div class="col-7">
								<div class="input-group">
									<input type="text" id="input-optionFilter" class="form-control" id="" placeholder="關鍵字">
									<select class="form-control hide" id="dept-type-selector">
										<option value="一般系所">一般系所</option>
										<option value="重點產業系所">重點產業系所</option>
									</select>
									<span class="input-group-btn">
										<button id="btn-manualSearch" class="btn btn-secondary" type="button">
											<i class="fa fa-search" aria-hidden="true"></i>
										</button>
									</span>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>

						<hr>

						<div class="row">
							<div class="col-12">
								<table class="table table-hover">
									<tbody id="optionalWish-list">
									</tbody>
								</table>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="row">
							<div class="col-12">
								<table class="table table-hover">
									<div id="pagination-container"></div>
								</table>
							</div>
						</div>

					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-xl-6">
				<div class="card card-bottom">
					<div class="card-header">已填選志願</div>
					<div class="card-body">
						<table class="table table-hover">
							<tbody id="wish-list">
							</tbody>
						</table>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<hr>

<div class="row">
	<div class="col-md text-center">
		<button id="btn-save" class="btn btn-primary" role="button">儲存</button>
	</div>
	<div class="col-md hide" id="div-btn-confirmed">
		<button id="btn-confirmed" class="btn btn-danger" role="button" >確認提交並鎖定志願</button>
	</div>
</div>


<div class="modal fade" id="warningModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="exampleModalCenterTitle" aria-hidden="true">
	<div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered" role="document">
		<div class="modal-content">
			<div class="modal-header">
				<i class="fa fa-3x fa-exclamation-circle" style="color:crimson; margin: 0 auto;" aria-hidden="true"></i>
				<br />
			</div>
			<div class="modal-body" style="color: royalblue; font-weight:600;" id="warningText">

			</div>
			<div class="modal-footer">
				<button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">返回填滿 70 個志願</button>
				<button type="button" id="secondConfirm" class="btn btn-primary" data-dismiss="modal">繼續</button>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="modal modal-centerd-lg" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" id="docs-modal">
	<div class="modal-dialog modal-lg modal-dialog-centerd" role="document">
	  <div class="modal-content">
		<div class="modal-header">
		  <h4 class="modal-title" id="modal-title"></h4>
		  <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
			<span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
		  </button>
		</div>
		<div class="modal-body" id='modal-body'>

		</div>
		<div class="modal-footer">
			<button type="button" class="btn btn-success" id="btn-info">詳細資訊</button>
		  <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">關閉</button>
		</div>
	  </div>
	</div>
  </div>

